{
  "texts": [
    "Hence, the number of rows in the embedding matrix is equal to the vocabulary size.",
    "The number of columns in the embedding matrix is equal to the dimension of the embedded token vector.",
    "GPT-3 trained a linear neural network to learn the matrix that converts the token symbols to number vectors.",
    "Intuition: After training, tokens with contextual similarity will have embedded vectors that are closer to each other in the embedding space and unrelated vectors will be further apart.",
    "The large dense vector makes the vector space sparce."
  ]
}